      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 39, United States Code, to provide that the payment of a bill, invoice, or statement of account due, if made by mail, shall be considered to have been made on the date as of which the envelope which is used to transmit such  payment is postmarked.</title>
